                    "line_text": "Sirène à qui nul ne résiste,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Semblait me dire : — « Dieu t'assiste,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Un jour ta peine finira. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "A lui je pensais ce matin ;\nJe me trouvais bien seul sur terre,\nEt je maudissais le destin\nQui m'accablait de sa colère !\nMais à sa fenêtre, Mira,\nSirène à qui nul ne résiste,\nSemblait me dire : — « Dieu t'assiste,\nUn jour ta peine finira. »"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "— « Non ! toujours, ai-je répondu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "J'aurai ma sombre inquiétude,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et dans la foule, confondu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Nul ne verra ma solitude !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
